START
    GATHERING the ingredients for pizza
    
    IF: the ingredients are complete 
      THEN
        Roll the dough and shape into a circle
        Bake for 10 to 15 minutes until the crust           is golden
      ADD
        the sauce and toppings
        Slice the pizza and serve

    ELSE:
      THEN
        Buy the rest ingredients
        Repeat the process from the beginning
END
